Lunar staff - pt1 is made by using a dramen staff on the Air Altar during the Lunar Diplomacy quest. After using the staff on the Fire Altar, Water Altar and Earth Altar (in that order), it becomes a lunar staff.

After the quest is complete, lunar staves can no longer be made through this process.

A player enchanting the dramen staff.
